item.description:
Last week, I posted and said the schedule would be that posts would happen Fridays. This week, thats happening the evening before. No matter. At least its happening and will be there for Friday.
So on with the show&hellip;
Since I am rebooting this blog, I thought it might be a good idea to first post about my interests in technology. This will give you a sense of what sorts of posts might be coming as we go from week to week.
